function render(){$("topSymbol").textContent=selected;$("clock").textContent=new Date().toLocaleTimeString("ar-SA");$("conn").textContent=err?err:live?.ok?"متصل بالبيانات الحية":"جاري الاتصال...";$("conn").className="pill "+(live?.ok?"good":"");$("view").innerHTML=view();document.querySelectorAll(".tab").forEach(b=>b.onclick=()=>{group=b.dataset.group;render()});document.querySelectorAll(".asset").forEach(b=>b.onclick=()=>{selected=b.dataset.symbol;history.replaceState(null,"",location.pathname+"?symbol="+encodeURIComponent(selected));live=null;err="";render();loadLive()})}
